You will be required to work as part of a team that oversees the planning and management of improvement works and programmes to ensure that Electrical Engineering installations and systems in HDB estates are in good working order. You should have a positive learning attitude, strong technical problem solving skills, with the keen interest to carry out feasibility studies on electrical transmission, control and distribution systems. You should also have good writing and communication skills.


Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.
